    <entry>
      <title>用Termux+Github+Hexo搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/58250.html"/>
      <url>/58250.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>由于我的电脑被我妈带走了，所以我也只能在手机上玩玩Termux。最近花了几天时间把博客框架换成了Hexo，心血来潮写了这篇教程</p><div class="note info flat"><p>本教程适用于Android端，理论上也适用于Linux端（毕竟都是Linux环境）</p></div><h1 id="Termux"><a href="#Termux" class="headerlink" title="Termux"></a>Termux</h1><blockquote><p>Termux是一款Android终端模拟器和Linux环境应用程序，无需root或设置即可直接运行。自动安装最小的基本系统，使用APT包管理器可以使用其他包。</p></blockquote><p>这是本次教程所用到的软件</p><h2 id="相关文档"><a href="#相关文档" class="headerlink" title="相关文档"></a>相关文档</h2><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="Termux官网" href="https://termux.com/"><div class="left"><img src="https://termux.com/favicon.ico"/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">Termux官网</p><p class="url">https://termux.com/</p></div></a></div><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="官方WiKi" href="https://wiki.termux.com/wiki/Main_Page"><div class="left"><img src="https://termux.com/favicon.ico"/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">官方WiKi</p><p class="url">https://wiki.termux.com/wiki/Main_Page</p></div></a></div><a class="ghcard" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/termux/termux-app"><img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/pin/?username=termux&repo=termux-app&show_owner=true"/></a> <h2 id="相关教程"><a href="#相关教程" class="headerlink" title="相关教程"></a>相关教程</h2><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="Termux高级终端安装使用配置教程" href="https://www.sqlsec.com/2018/05/termux.html"><div class="left"><img src="https://image.3001.net/images/20210606/16229390604952.png"/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">Termux高级终端安装使用配置教程</p><p class="url">https://www.sqlsec.com/2018/05/termux.html</p></div></a></div><h2 id="下载地址"><a href="#下载地址" class="headerlink" title="下载地址"></a>下载地址</h2><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="F-Droid下载" href="https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux/"><div class="left"><img src="https://f-droid.org/assets/fdroid-logo-text_S0MUfk_FsnAYL7n2MQye-34IoSNm6QM6xYjDnMqkufo=.svg"/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">F-Droid下载</p><p class="url">https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux/</p></div></a></div><p>博主不推荐使用其它下载方式，F-Droid下载的版本较新</p><details class="folding-tag" red><summary> 遇到问题？ </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>第一次启动Termux的时候需要从远程服务器加载数据，你可能会遇到一个弹窗<br><img src="https://image.3001.net/images/20200418/15871943464391.png" alt="Ubable to install"><br>解决方法：</p><ol><li>开飞机（懂得都懂），成功率高</li><li>切换到运营商流量，有概率成功</li></ol>              </div>            </details><h1 id="安装Vim"><a href="#安装Vim" class="headerlink" title="安装Vim"></a>安装Vim</h1><p>Vim是一个Linux编辑器，，基本上Linux发行版都会自带Vim</p><p>非必要安装，但这东西以后要用到</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install vim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h1><p>Hexo是用Nodejs编写的，首先需要安装Nodejs。在Termux里输入以下命令安装Nodejs长期稳定版本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install nodejs-lts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看看有没有安装成功吧</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -V</span><br><span class="line">npm -V</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完Nodejs后，你就可以使用npm命令来安装Hexo了</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="本地运行"><a href="#本地运行" class="headerlink" title="本地运行"></a>本地运行</h1><p>先创建一个目录，并初始化Hexo环境</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> hexo </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> hexo</span><br><span class="line">hexo init  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>命令中<code>mkdir</code>就是创建一个目录，后面的参数就是目录名，可自行更改；<code>cd</code>就是切换到一个目录，后面的参数就是你前面创建的目录的名称</p><p>现在一个简单的博客就创建好了，运行以下命令让Hexo在本地跑起来吧</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s      </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问<code>http://127.0.0.1:4000</code>就可以看到效果</p><p><img src="https://image.3001.net/images/20180502/1525190501582.png" alt="Hexo本地运行效果"></p><p>如果想退出本地运行，就 <kbd>CTRL</kbd> + <kbd>C</kbd></p><h1 id="部署到Github"><a href="#部署到Github" class="headerlink" title="部署到Github"></a>部署到Github</h1><p>先安装git和ssh</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt install git</span><br><span class="line">apt install openssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再生成ssh key</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;Github用户名&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;Github注册邮箱&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;Github注册邮箱&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行以上命令后，一直回车，然后会在<code>~/.ssh</code>目录里生成一个<code>id_rsa.pub</code>文件，使用Vim打开它并复制</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开<a href="https://github.com/settings/keys"></a>，跟着步骤来</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/21/qPbeHyKWBLJVn2l.jpg" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/21/jNBnX9qGp85Zsfd.jpg" alt=""></p><p>然后在博客根目录安装<code>hexo-deployer-git</code>插件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着用Vim打开<code>_config.yml</code>文件，找到并修改为</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:Github用户名/仓库名.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行一键三连上传到Github即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在访问<code>Github用户名.github.io</code>就可以看到你的博客了</p><div class="note blue icon flat"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>下次出一个Hexo切换主题的教程</p></div><h1 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h1><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="Termux高级终端安装使用配置教程" href="https://www.sqlsec.com/2018/05/termux.html"><div class="left"><img src="https://image.3001.net/images/20210606/16229390604952.png"/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">Termux高级终端安装使用配置教程</p><p class="url">https://www.sqlsec.com/2018/05/termux.html</p></div></a></div><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="Termux搭建hexo博客并部署到GitHub" href="https://www.cnblogs.com/fak3/p/15812949.html"><div class="left"><img src="https://common.cnblogs.com/favicon.svg"/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">Termux搭建hexo博客并部署到GitHub</p><p class="url">https://www.cnblogs.com/fak3/p/15812949.html</p></div></a></div>]]></content>
      
      
